**Token Origin Key**
рџџЈ `KEYWORD` вЂ” `_scan_identifier()` + `KEYWORDS` lookup
рџџў `IDENTIFIER` вЂ” `_scan_identifier()` + lookup miss
рџџЎ `GREATER_EQUAL` вЂ” `_match('=')` True В· maximal munch
рџ”µ punctuation/operator вЂ” `SINGLE_CHAR_TOKENS[ch]`
рџ”µ `NUMBER` вЂ” `_scan_number()` integer path
в¬њ `EOF` вЂ” appended by `scan_tokens()` post-loop
---
**Column derivation** (source length = 30 chars)
`if`=1 В· `(`=4 В· `x`=5 В· `>=`=7вЂ“8 В· `42`=10вЂ“11
`)`=12 В· `{`=14 В· `return`=16вЂ“21 В· `true`=23вЂ“26
`;`=27 В· `}`=29 В· EOF.col = 31 (after 30 advances)
'| {
    style.font-size: 11
