invariants: |'md'
**Test Invariants**
В· Exactly 11 non-EOF tokens
В· Exactly 1 EOF token, always last
В· Zero ERROR tokens in clean input
В· Every `Token.column` = position of first character
В· Changing any expected value = changing the language spec
